wmdockapps
==========


This is a collection of dock applications for the Window Maker window manager.

The dockapps have been updated to run under WindowMaker-0.95.7 on Ubuntu-16.10.

The collection consists of the following apps:

	wmclock - analog clock
	wmmute - volume control


To install, please change the PREFIX in the toplevel Makefile and then type:

	sudo make install

(or, make install as root).

Pr. default applications are stored in /usr/local/bin with manpages with in
/usr/local/man/man1.

Browse through the man pages to see what each program do ...

Enjoy!

Brian
